---

---

<div class="nb-card">
  <div class="nb-inner">

    <div class="nb-front">
      <div class="front-header">
        <div class="front-tag">Experiencia laboral</div>
        <p class="company-name">Ecoregistry</p>
        <p class="company-sub">Carbon Credits Platform</p>
      </div>
      <div class="front-body">
        <div class="meta-row">
          <div class="meta-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 1a7 7 0 1 0 0 14A7 7 0 0 0 8 1zm.75 7.5H5.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.5h2.5V4a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v4a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="meta-label">Duración</p>
            <p class="meta-value">1 año</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-row">
          <div class="meta-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 0C5.24 0 3 2.24 3 5c0 3.75 5 11 5 11s5-7.25 5-11c0-2.76-2.24-5-5-5zm0 7a2 2 0 1 1 0-4 2 2 0 0 1 0 4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="meta-label">Ubicación</p>
            <p class="meta-value">Medellín, Colombia</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-row">
          <div class="meta-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2 3h12v2H2zm0 4h8v2H2zm0 4h10v2H2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="meta-label">Sector</p>
            <p class="meta-value">Sostenibilidad &amp; MRV</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="front-footer">
        <span class="hover-hint">Ver experiencia</span>
        <span class="hover-arrow">→</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nb-back">
      <div class="back-title">Lo que hice</div>
      <ul class="back-list">
        <li>Diseñé y desarrollé funcionalidades para una plataforma MRV de certificación de créditos de carbono.</li>
        <li>Construí interfaces en React para vistas complejas de datos.</li>
        <li>Desarrollé y mantuve APIs RESTful con Node.js / Express.</li>
        <li>Resolví bugs críticos mejorando la estabilidad de la plataforma.</li>
        <li>Colaboré con stakeholders internacionales en Asia para soluciones técnicas a medida.</li>
        <li>Participé en planificación ágil y priorización de tareas.</li>
        <li>Creé herramientas de web scraping con Python y Selenium.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="back-badge-row">
        <span class="back-badge">React</span>
        <span class="back-badge">Node.js</span>
        <span class="back-badge">Python</span>
        <span class="back-badge">REST API</span>
        <span class="back-badge">Selenium</span>
        <span class="back-badge">Agile</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .nb-card {
    width: 340px;
    height: 480px;
    perspective: 1200px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }
  .nb-inner {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    transform: rotate(-5deg);
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
  }
  .nb-card:hover .nb-inner {
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
  }
  .nb-front, .nb-back {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    border-radius: 0px;
    border: 5px solid #1a1a1a;
    box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px #1a1a1a;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  .nb-front {
    background: #f5f0e8;
    transform: rotateY(0deg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .nb-back {
    background: #f5f0e8;
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 24px 22px;
  }

  .front-header {
    background: #2d5a3d;
    padding: 20px 22px 16px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
  }
  .front-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #a8e063;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .company-name {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #f5f0e8;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .company-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #a8e063;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .front-body {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .meta-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .meta-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
  .meta-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: #2d5a3d;
    border: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .meta-icon svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #a8e063; }
  .meta-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #555;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0 2px;
  }
  .meta-value {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .front-footer {
    background: #a8e063;
    border-top: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .hover-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.07em;
  }
  .hover-arrow {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .back-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.09em;
    color: #2d5a3d;
    border-bottom: 2.5px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .back-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 9px;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .back-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .back-list li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: #2d5a3d;
    border: 1.5px solid #1a1a1a;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .back-badge-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 5px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    border-top: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    padding-top: 11px;
  }
  .back-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border: 1.5px solid #1a1a1a;
    background: #a8e063;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
</style>